<p>Erebus is an Open Source RPG (Role-Playing Game), for PCs, smartphones, tablets and handhelds.</p>

<p>This is currently under development and in its early stages, though
already playable with three quests, as well as having randomly
generated dungeons to explore.</p>

<p>
<!-- we use explicit full URLs, as when people view this locally on the readmes that come with the archive, they won't have the screenshots locally! -->
